      <title>首相顾问称日本必须做好应对特朗普关税的准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-12/advisor-to-pm-says-japan-must-brace-for-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[（观看）：首相石破茂的国家安全顾问表示，日本需要为候任总统唐纳德·特朗普承诺的关税做好准备。长岛昭久周四在接受彭博社独家采访时表示，他在最近访问美国期间与特朗普团队成员就关税问题进行了“坦诚”的讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-12/advisor-to-pm-says-japan-must-brace-for-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 23:56:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>晨星称，实力较弱的私人债务借款人将遭受更大伤害</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/weaker-private-debt-borrowers-to-see-more-hurt-morningstar-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[晨星报告称，评级较低的私人信贷借款人预计明年将“继续陷入困境”，因为他们面临销售额下滑、利润率下降和借贷成本高昂的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/weaker-private-debt-borrowers-to-see-more-hurt-morningstar-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 23:39:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>制裁前景抵消供应过剩影响，油价有望周线上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国可能对伊朗和俄罗斯实施更严厉的制裁，抵消了人们对明年全球石油供应大幅过剩的持续担忧，油价每周均上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 23:30:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
