    <item>
      <title>新西兰请求美国停止对特朗普征收新关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/new-zealand-pleads-case-with-us-for-no-new-tariffs-under-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰财政部长尼古拉威利斯表示，新西兰认为，美国当选总统唐纳德特朗普上任后可能对新西兰征收任何全面关税，新西兰应该获得豁免，并已指示官员说明理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/new-zealand-pleads-case-with-us-for-no-new-tariffs-under-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 22:30:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲利率下降，为特朗普时代再来做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/europe-s-rates-head-lower-in-readiness-for-another-trump-era</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲各国央行正坚决采取鸽派政策，以帮助各经济体应对唐纳德·特朗普第二次入主白宫可能带来的更多混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/europe-s-rates-head-lower-in-readiness-for-another-trump-era</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 18:12:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国誓言明年加大财政支出以刺激消费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/china-signals-more-fiscal-stimulus-rate-cuts-to-boost-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，2025年将增加公共借贷和支出，并将政策重点转向消费，以期在即将实施的美国关税威胁出口的情况下修复经济的薄弱环节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/china-signals-more-fiscal-stimulus-rate-cuts-to-boost-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 11:17:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
